// SPDX-License-Identifier: AGPL-3.0-or-later
/// CoinJoin.sol - stablecoin token adapter
// This contract is forked from MakerDAO's join.sol - DaiJoin contract
// Copyright (C) 2018 Rain <rainbreak@riseup.net>
//
